words: I had been obsessed with Harry Potter, er, have been obsessed with Harry Potter since I
was in third grade. Um, and once the new, uh, Harry
Potter World opened up in Universal Studios in Floria, Florida, my friend and I

And then, the spring break of my junior year, so last year in
twenty fifteen, um, uh, we had plans, and we made it happen.

and, uh, plane ticket for myself and hotel, and the tickets to the park.
Um, and we flew to Florida, and I just remember, that whole trip,
being insanely happy about everything that was going on, and just, um,
feeling very proud of myself because I had worked so hard, um, to get that

And, uh, we walked through the park, and then we, when we went,
when we actually went into Harry Potter World on the first day, it was just like nothing I had ever seen before
because it was something that I was so, um, passionate about. Just
passionate about the books and the characters, and anything, and just walking down and seeing how

and then we were able to spend three days in the park, and there are two Harry Potter
